author: brane
msg: Merge the r1697381 group from trunk:
Make 'svnfsfs load-index' work as advertised in the documentation
svnfsfs load-index would only ever be used in high-stress situations
like desaster recovery.  So, while workarounds are possible, having
people jump though a few extra hoops is a bad thing in that context.
r1697381 - fixes the revision rewriting code (only used by this tool)
r1697384 - Makes dump format match expected input format
r1697387 - Implement sorting of the columns on input
BH: Some tests around this would make this much easier to review.
